{
  "stem": "13693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The center of this town was completely destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we are working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was working over there for [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is for [NON-ENGLISH] organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And now I will the two stories-- what happened in [NON-ENGLISH] and what happened afterwards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were building a depot for the trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And once upon a time, I was working-- I was working in the depot, and I brought-- and while I was going to work, I saw a group of Jewish girls, about 17, working as a-- we call this a brigade-- a brigade, to work.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from nowhere, we saw the two young German soldiers were laying around, and were-- were target practicing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were shoot with dum-dum bullets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they killed all 17.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the bodies were flying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were just pass them by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the blood and everything splashed all over in the ravines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This a picture what still stays in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is the same day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This is '42.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This was the winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This was already-- the German didn't feel so good about this time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Went in to [NON-ENGLISH] organization and while building in here, I brought in to my German engineer a long four-by-four.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He takes the four-by-four, hits me over my head, knocks me in my teeth, knocks me unconscious-- luckily-- and leave me over there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Luckily, he left me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Some of the guys came in later, and let me stand up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I lost my front teeth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A little while later-- this was probably two, three months-- the Jews were still over there-- about 18,000, 17,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Lida ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Lida ghetto was not really a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a big track-- same track.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this one side were the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
